675D15F7.Line3.126500: We’ve survived, yes. But I’m not sure this place will hold out for much longer.

8ED96C35.Line1.126500: Crusaders used to keep us safe. But they’ve gone and started dying off. Folks are scared, looking to leave. Hell, so am I.

FB3FFC35.MenuLabel: “How does Zarbinzet survive in a place so unforgiving?”
